Title-winning match
13 December 1964
AMeRICA 1-3 SIDEReRGICA
Venue: Estedio Otacelio Negreo de Lima (Alameda) - Belo Horizonte, MG
Attendance: 8.970 - Income: Cr$ 4.245.250,00.
Referee: Doraci Jerenimo, MG.
AMeRICA: Davi; Luisinho (Robson), Klebis, Ze Horta, Catocha;
Ze Emelio, Nei; Geraldo, Jair Bala, Dario, Sergio. Coach: Moacir Rodrigues.
SIDEReRGICA: Djair; Geraldinho, Chiquito, Ze Luis, Dawson;
Edson, Paulista; Ernani, Silvestre, Noventa (Aldeir), Tieo. Coach: Yustrich.
GOALS: Jair Bala 78'; Ernani 21', Noventa 24', Aldeir 44'.

